Sol, the sunlit chef - Wizard Alchemist (Brewmaster) 

Consumes copious amount of alcohol and other alchemical drinks
Always experimenting trying out sips of various drinks (flavour not of any use)

10 mins to brew?
What is the advantage of brewing a spell into a potion?
  More uses, save across days, longer lasting, more potent?

"The grill stick"
Trident as a staff with trash stats
Can get 3 fish over the stove on the trident

Brewmaster's kit
Poisoner's kit (but with tankards)
Includes the vials, chemicals, and other equipment necessary for the creation of poisons. Proficiency with this kit lets you add your proficiency bonus to any ability checks you make to craft or use poisons.


